---
import ProjectLayout from "../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro";
import Badge from "../../components/Badge.astro";
---

<ProjectLayout title="Haxball AI">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <main>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Haxball AI</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          A machine learning-powered search bot that helps users find the best
          products within a category based on their criteria.
        </p>
        <img
          alt="LLM Search Bot"
          src="/placeholder.svg"
          width="600"
          height="200"
          class="w-full aspect-[3/1] object-cover"
        />
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The LLM Search Bot is designed to simplify the product search process
          by understanding natural language inputs and providing personalized
          recommendations. The bot utilizes a large language model to interpret
          user queries and match them with the most relevant products from a
          comprehensive database.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">How It Works</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Natural Language Processing</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              The bot processes the user's search query using advanced natural
              language processing techniques to understand the intent and
              context behind the request.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Product Matching</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              The bot then searches a curated database of products to find the
              best matches based on the user's criteria, leveraging machine
              learning algorithms to rank and prioritize the results.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Personalized Recommendations</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              Finally, the bot presents the user with a list of products that
              best fit their needs, taking into account their previous
              preferences and behavior to provide personalized suggestions.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Continuous Improvement</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              The bot's algorithms are constantly being refined and updated to
              improve the accuracy and relevance of the search results, ensuring
              an ever-better user experience.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Technologies Used</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <Badge>Python</Badge>
          <Badge>Machine Learning</Badge>
          <Badge>NLP</Badge>
          <Badge>scikit-learn</Badge>
          <Badge>Django</Badge>
          <Badge>PostgreSQL</Badge>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Challenges Faced</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          One of the main challenges was optimizing the search algorithm to
          handle ambiguous queries and still provide accurate results. Another
          challenge was ensuring the bot could scale to accommodate a growing
          product database without compromising performance.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Outcome</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          The LLM Search Bot successfully launched and has been helping users
          make informed purchasing decisions. Feedback has been overwhelmingly
          positive, with users appreciating the ease of use and accuracy of the
          search results.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Project Roadmap</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Short-Term Goals</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Improve natural language processing capabilities</li>
              <li>Expand product database coverage</li>
              <li>Enhance user interface and user experience</li>
              <li>Implement real-time product updates</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Long-Term Goals</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
              <li>Integrate with e-commerce platforms</li>
              <li>Develop mobile applications</li>
              <li>Implement personalized recommendations</li>
              <li>Expand to international markets</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Project Highlights</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Accurate Search Results</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              The LLM Search Bot's advanced natural language processing
              capabilities allow it to understand complex queries and provide
              highly accurate product recommendations.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500"
              >
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-green-500 font-medium">Verified by users</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Scalable Infrastructure</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              The bot's underlying infrastructure is designed to handle a
              growing product database and user base without compromising
              performance.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500"
              >
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-green-500 font-medium"
                >Tested for high-volume usage</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">User Testimonials</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700">
              "The LLM Search Bot has completely transformed my product search
              experience. I'm able to find exactly what I need with just a few
              natural language queries."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="flex items-center mt-4 space-x-2">
              <img
                alt="User Avatar"
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full"
                src="/placeholder.svg"
              />
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">Jane Doe</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <blockquote class="text-gray-700">
              "I'm amazed by the accuracy of the LLM Search Bot's
              recommendations. It's saved me so much time and hassle in finding
              the perfect products for my needs."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="flex items-center mt-4 space-x-2">
              <img
                alt="User Avatar"
                class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full"
                src="/placeholder.svg"
              />
              <span class="text-gray-700 font-medium">John Smith</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</ProjectLayout>
